properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 13 at 6:59PM EST until January 14 at 12:00PM EST by NWS Wilmington NC
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility as low as 1/4 MN or
less.

* WHERE...Waters from Surf City to Cape Fear NC from 20 to 40
nm, Waters from Cape Fear NC to Little River Inlet SC from 20
to 40 nm, Waters from Little River Inlet to Murrells Inlet SC
from 20 to 40 nm and Waters from Surf City NC to South Santee
River SC from 20 to 40 nm.

* WHEN...Until noon EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON EST TUESDAY
